metadata.name: Buckets Club Front Nine #1
metadata.description: Buckets Club Front Nine is an NFT project consisting of 3D unique characters based on the iconic Buckets logo from Malbon Golf. By holding a Front Nine, it grants you access to the tournaments that we host, which are exclusive to only Buckets Club holders. Additionally, you will gain access to our token-gated website. Owners are part of the most exclusive digital country club with real-world utility and added value that grows over time, with full transparency on the Ethereum blockchain.
